Customers have indicated that, many times an answer to a question resides within a Confluence page. Therefore the _answerer_ wants to be able to include the page in his/her answer. A page excerpt would be fine too.

This is particularly helpful for seeding Questions with content when you're first starting out.

Can we enable the {include-page} or {excerpt-include} macro for answers and possible questions?

